Dim1: Patient representative appointed to governing board in hospitals
Report on patient safety performance published every year
Governement endorsed and signed WHO charter on health worker safety: a priority for patient safety
Patient safety included in undergraduate professional education curricula
National target set for reduction in medication-related harm
National patient safety action plan developed
Health care facilities participate in patient safety incidence reporting and learning system
Reporting system for never events (sentinel events) in place
Targets established for health care-associated infections
